# DD-1: CI/CD Enforcement
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: All builds and deployments

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- CI/CD: Continuous Integration and Continuous Deployment pipeline.

ENFORCE: No deployment may proceed without all CI/CD pipeline checks passing.
PROHIBIT: Skipping pipeline checks; ignoring failed test results.
ON VIOLATION: Halt deployment → notify orchestrator and DevOps personnel.
